# Steps taken to install SASS:

1. Navigate to the alx-intermediate-frontend directory:
   $ cd alx-intermediate-frontend

2. Create a new directory 0x03-sass_scss:
   $ mkdir 0x03-sass_scss

3. Install Node.js using nvm:
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   $ source ~/.bashrc

4. Install Node.js version 20.16:
   $ nvm install 20.16

5. Install SASS globally:
   $ npm install -g sass@3.7.4

6. Verify the SASS installation:
   $ sass --version
